@ExpansionPunks does a great job to improve diversity from @cryptopunksbot and @DApeWives offers diversity from @BoredApeYC, though would love to see more female integration in all projects from the start!
We have such a great opportunity on the building groud up to correct past biases and improve inclusion from the start. #WAGMI and let's work together to make the space feel welcome to all!
For example, if the #NFT team is giving away a @ROLEX, also give away a @CHANEL purse. If your #PFP avatar art features only menswear, diversify with some dresses.
So many #PFP #NFT projects could benefit from adding a few more female characteristics and projects, and cater prizes and rewards that attract wider demographics.
To get more #womenincrypto, we need to integrate #Diversity in more projects to better reflect the world we live in, not just have separate female-only collections.
